  "texts": [
    "Addressing these errors required the provision of contextual information in addition to the instructions.",
    "The contextual information was developed iteratively in the same manner as the prompts.The LLM was initially not very successful at writing an executable R script or choosing the correct model to use for the analysis, for either outcome type.",
    "For example, the LLM sometimes invented R packages and functions that it included in the script.",
    "Including worked examples has previously been shown to improve the performance of LLMs in multi-step reasoning tasks [21].",
    "Therefore, we provided an example script appropriate for the type of analysis needed, as contextual information for the LLM."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Including worked examples has previously been shown to improve the performance of LLMs in multi-step reasoning tasks [21]."
  ]
